5. Changes to be Implemented

After analyzing these 33 data points, the following changes are recommended for
the next development phase:
Frontend UI Cleanup: Cut Navbar vertical padding in half and implement a
sticky header.
Back-end Database Design Changes: Include a status flag on orders to indicate
delivery/collection status.
User Interface Redesign: Use an <input> instead of "dropdown-content" on the CSS
Grid system to create product cards.
Accessibility Audit: Move away from a strong green color scheme (for instance,
#2d5a27) as it hinders text legibility.
